Marie-France Pisier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie-France_Pisier 0 Marie-France Pisier (10 May 1944 – 24 April 2011) was a French actress, screenwriter, and director. She appeared in numerous films of the French New Wave and twice earned the national César Award for Best Supporting Actress.
